the issuance of the following debt securities 
by The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. (the         
“Company”) on December 6, 2021 pursuant to the
Company’s shelf registration statement on Form
S-3(File No. 333-253421)(as amended, the      
“Registration Statement”):

       2023 (the “Floating Rate Securities”)

       (the “Fixed Rate Securities”)
